    We don't even use analytics - we respect your privacy completely.
  </p>
</div>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>1. What We Don't Collect</h2>
  <p>
    Nahlawi Tools is designed with <strong>absolute privacy</strong> as the foundation. We:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>âœ… <strong>No cookies</strong> (except dark mode preference stored locally)</li>
