    <li>Announce the change prominently on the homepage</li>
    <li>Only use privacy-first services (no Google Analytics, no ad trackers)</li>
    <li>Make it completely optional (opt-in, not opt-out)</li>
    <li>Continue to keep all tool processing local in your browser</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    <strong>Our commitment:</strong> Your data will NEVER be sold, shared, or used 
    for any purpose other than improving the tools you love.
  </p>
</section>

